    {
      "code": "M15-E-VCG03",
      "label": "God's sovereign purposive counsel (ya.ats: divine planning)",
      "context_description": "The term names the divine counsel as irresistible sovereign intent — 'as I have planned, so shall it be; as I have purposed, so shall it stand' (Isa 14:24). God's ya.ats is unalterable: no one counselled him (Isa 40:14), his counsel against nations will stand, and the Messiah is the Wonderful Counselor whose inner wisdom directs his people. Inner-being phenomenon: divine sovereign purposive counsel.",
